text: The Los Angeles County Board of Supervisors (LACBOS) is the five-member governing body of Los Angeles County, California, United States. ==Current Supervisors== Members of the Board are officially nonpartisan, and are elected by constituents of their respective districts. As of 2020, they are: File:HLS Headshot.jpg|Hilda Solis District 1 since 2014 File:Mitchell Holly.jpg|Holly Mitchell District 2 since 2020 File:Sheila Kuehl (4226269624).jpg|Sheila Kuehl District 3 since 2014 File:SupervisorHahn.jpg|Janice Hahn District 4 since 2016 File:Supervisor Kathryn Barger.jpg|Kathryn Barger District 5 since 2016 ==References== Category:Los Angeles County, California
